# Historical test results directory
# This directory stores archived test runs for trend analysis

# Structure:
# - run-YYYYMMDD-HHMMSS/
#   - summary.json
#   - l0-results.json
#   - l1-results.json
#   - l2-results.json
#   - l3-results.json
#   - l4-results.json
#   - differential-results.json

# Retention: Last 100 runs are kept
# Older runs are automatically pruned by continuous-test-runner.sh
